{"tid":1029350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【真支爆】2個百厭星塞炮仗入車頭 引擎越燒越大火","createTime":"2019-02-20T07:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T07:44:00.000Z","uid":150685,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ddd03307fa383ae25c8388b3b820b81c50708eb6","tid":1029350,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:31:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190219/large/1550590328_8bdb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190219%2Flarge%2F1550590328_8bdb.jpg&h=49cd9733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地頑童的惡作劇，越來越離譜！雲南昭通日前有兩名小孩，在街上玩耍時將點着的炮仗塞進一輛私家車的車頭裏，幾分鐘後該輛汽車的引擎，疑被炮仗燒着開始冒出火苗，火勢隨後越來越大。幸虧有路人經過，發現後及時打電話求助，但車輛被燒，已令車主遭受巨大損失。<br />\n<br />\n內地媒體並沒有交代，警方事後有否找出這兩名小疑犯，但有網友指，「縱火應該追究法律責任，未成年兒童雖然不承擔刑事責任，但是監護人應該賠償損失。」亦有網友稱，這證明內地「教育出了問題」、「家庭教育的缺失」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190220/59277495\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190220%2F59277495&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n81znTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=5d32b752\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190220%2F59277495&h=284644ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190220/59277495</a>"},{"pid":"f40756cf20028be54615fdb543cafb4148a407cd","tid":1029350,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:33:30.000Z","msg":"點解唔塞落油缸"},{"pid":"7b4a267c297af4cf60c79f9328ae58ad522dca06","tid":1029350,"uid":16960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:34:56.000Z","msg":"沒事的 他只是個小孩"},{"pid":"8b60ed7708198764b171c53536ff44db7ec5df4d","tid":1029350,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:39:14.000Z","msg":"火燒旺車呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gi